abstract: The company, whose chief executive endorsed Barack Obama during the campaign, is having an inaugural ball in Washington to welcome the new administration.

lead_paragraph: Google, whose chief executive endorsed Barack Obama during the campaign, is having a party when Mr. Obama takes office.

headline.main: For Inauguration, Google Plans a Party to Cross Party Lines
